6
00:00:11,611 --> 00:00:13,602
如果监狱是你设计的 就有可能
Not if you designed the place, it isn't.

7
00:00:34,200 --> 00:00:35,428
门最好是开的
It better be open, bro.

8
00:00:35,602 --> 00:00:38,537
